# RazoarPay Clone 

This is a clone of the Razorpay payment gateway, built using HTML and Tailwind CSS.

## Node Module Missing

**Note: This project requires Node.js and the necessary modules to run.**

If you encounter the error message "Node module not found" or any related issues, it means that the required Node modules are missing. Follow the instructions below to resolve this:

1. Make sure you have Node.js installed on your machine. You can download it from [https://nodejs.org](https://nodejs.org) and follow the installation instructions for your operating system.

2. Once Node.js is installed, open a command prompt or terminal and navigate to the project folder.

3. Run the following command to install the required Node modules:

```bash
npm install



After the installation is complete, run the project using the following command:

npm start
